dct_title_s: Automobile road from Los Angeles to San Diego via Riverside Elsinore Fallbrook and Escondido
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; A.J.W.
Relief shown by hachures and text (grade percentage).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and San Diego.
Numbered 199 in lower right, 4 in upper left, and 15 in left margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
